data.text: As Vice President of Finance & Accounting, Brian is responsible for financial management of the entire Emerald portfolio with a core focus in financial reporting, management of the accounts payable function, cash flow projections, and coordination of the annual budget process. Brian also assists the Human Resources department with the administration and annual renewal of the of Emeraldâ€™s group insurance plans. Prior to joining Emerald, Brian spent 8 years as a financial analyst with National City and PNC Bank. Brian has a BBA in Accounting from Cleveland State University.
